data.description:
COMING SOON!  

WORKING ON MINOR REPAIRS AND LANDSCAPING.  YOUR OWN SECLUDED PARADISE ON 2.18 ACRES YET ONLY 5 MILES FROM PROVIDENCE - CRAFTSMAN STYLE HOME WITH FRONT PORCH SWINGS - COVERED BACK PORCH - FRESH NEUTRAL GRAY PAINT THROUGHOUT HOME WITH WHITE TRIM - GRANITE, STAINLESS APPLIANCES - HARDWOOD AND TILE FLOORS - MASSIVE BONUS - BEAUTIFUL BACKYARD LIVING AREA - NEW ROOF 2019 - NEW WATER HEATERS 2017 - SEMI IN GROUND SALT WATER POOL - BEAUTIFUL NEW HANDICAP ACCESSIBLE POOL/GUEST HOUSE/IN-LAW APT BUILT IN 2019 WITH LIVING/KITCHEN AREA, BEDROOM AREA, MASSIVE CLOSET AND BATHROOM W/ PERSONAL CARPORT AREA, FRENCH DOORS OPEN UP TO COVERED POOL DECK WITH TIN ROOF - 3 BAY MATCHING CARPORT ALMOST COMPLETE ADDED IN JAN 2020. ATTACHED 2 CAR GARAGE IS TILED, HEATED AND COOLED. AWESOME MUDROOM/LAUNDRY ROOM ENTRY FROM GARAGE WITH PLENTY OF CUBBY SPACE FOR SHOES/BACKPACKS, PLENTY OF CABINETRY FOR CLEANING SUPPLIES. SCREENED IN BACK PORCH PERFECT FOR AFTERNOON NAPS. CEILING FANS IN ALL ROOMS - MASTER BATH WHIRPOOL JET TUB HAS TV BUILT INTO WALL FOR VIEWING FROM BATH. MASTER BEDROOM CABIN FEEL WITH WOOD CEILING - LARGE ATTIC FOR STORAGE - SHED THAT MATCHES HOME OUT BACK FOR MOWER/STORAGE.  SENTRICON TERMITE SYSTEM.  Until home is ready to show, please email pjjposborne@gmail.com with any questions and I will return your email as soon as I can.  I CANNOT ANSWER OR RETURN PHONE CALLS AT THIS TIME.
data.whatILove: Everything!  It's so different than any other house out there for sale.  Craftsman style home with front porch and swings. Close to Providence (less than 10 minute drive), close to Long Hunter State Park, walking trail to Percy Priest Lake, beautiful treed lot, wonderful fire pit area out back.  Favorite room is the bonus room which is massive and has a stacked stone wall for the mounted 75" TV.  Love that this neighborhood is somewhat hidden, has large lots and no "thru" traffic.  Easy access to I-40 or I-24 via Mount Juliet Road or Hobson Pike.
